---
title: Pork Rigatoni in Tomato Sauce  with spinach and sprinkled cheese
description: This is a simple dish at first glance, but it's also filled with flavour. Featuring succulent pork, rich tomato sauce and al dente rigatoni, you'll find your tummy and your tastebuds more than satisfied with this quick and easy meal.
